<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../366/18366.xml">
Lycos</link></company>
 Internet <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../023/4059023.xml">
search engine</link> company. He developed the Lycos Search Engine while working on the <artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<instrumentality wordnetid="103575240" confidence="0.8">
<engine wordnetid="103287733" confidence="0.8">
<motor wordnetid="103789946" confidence="0.8">
